type: software
title: "MHN AI Agent Memory"
abstract: >-
  Associative memory for AI agents using Modern Hopfield Networks.
  Replaces LLM-plus-database memory pipelines with a single matrix multiply
  backed by the Ramsauer et al. (2021) update rule.
